title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Claim the Albany Fränken Stange
content:
Venture out to sea, sneak aboard a loaded container ship, and make off with the goods in The Cargo Ship Robbery — including a customized Albany Fränken Stange (Sports Classic) with the option to claim it as your own Personal Vehicle just in time for spooky season.

Other Salvage Yard Robbery Targets: Pegassi Torero (Sports Classic) | Albany Hermes (Muscle)
